public abstract class AbstractObjectAttribute
extends java.lang.Object
implements DefUseVariable

This abstract DefUseVariable represents a field of an object being accessed by a method.

Constructor Detail

AbstractObjectAttribute

public AbstractObjectAttribute(Method method,
                               long instantiationNumber)
Construct the abstract DefUseVariable representing a field of an object.

Please note that this is an internal data-structure, not to be used without the handling of def-use chains. For performance reasons no checks are done.

Parameters:
method - The Method reading from or writing to the field.
instantiationNumber - The consecutive instantiation number of the object.
